parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Passenger Airbag Seat Occupancy Sensor Mat Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag seat occupancy sensor mat can cause the passenger airbag to malfunction, potentially leading to injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The "pass airbag off" light goes on
warning of a malfunction in the passenger restraint system
and the passenger airbag may not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of Takata airbag recall parts can leave vehicles with potentially faulty airbags, putting occupants at risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: None
as the issue is related to the unavailability of recall parts
not a specific malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and overheating can cause the vehicle to lose power and come to a sudden stop, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
especially when accelerating or driving uphill
the temperature gauge may not show an overheating condition
but the vehicle displays an "overheating" message
the engine may race out of control
and the vehicle may not shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fuel system malfunction can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The engine stalls
especially when driving at high speeds
the vehicle may display a "fuel system malfunction" message
the vehicle may not start
and the battery may drain due to repeated attempts to start the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The VANOS system failure can cause the engine to stall or lose power, potentially leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The engine stalls
an abnormal noise is emitted from the vehicle
the VANOS bolts may be loose or fractured.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag Failure and Steering System Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy and the detachment of the steering wheel can lead to severe injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash.
symptoms: No airbag deployment
steering wheel detachment
seat collapse
and failure of safety features to protect occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure and Power Steering Loss
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of electrical power and power steering can cause the vehicle to become difficult to control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Sudden loss of power
"Charging Malfunction" warning
difficulty turning the vehicle
and heavy steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Power System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The random stalling of the engine can cause the loss of power steering and power brake assist, leading to hazardous driving situations.
symptoms: Engine stalling
power steering failure
power brake assist failure
and difficulty controlling the vehicle.
